### Industry-specific content restrictions (MANDATORY)

**[IF medical / healthcare]:**
- No unverified health claims (cure, treat, reverse, heal, prevent disease)
- Disclaimers required on any outcome-suggestive content
- No before/after imagery without documented patient consent
- Regulatory-aware terminology (EU MDR, FDA, local health authority)

**[IF food & bev]:**
- Allergens listed per local law (EU Reg 1169/2011 or equivalent)
- No health claims beyond approved list (EU Reg 432/2012)
- Origin claims (PDO, PGI, DOC, AVA, AOC) verified before use
- [If alcohol:] Age-gate on site, no minors in marketing, responsible drinking messaging

**[IF finance / investment]:**
- No "investment advice" unless licensed
- No "guaranteed returns" ever
- Past performance disclaimer on any historical return figure
- Client testimonials used only when permitted by regulator

**[IF family office]:**
- Default posture: no public content
- Any exception requires explicit principal sign-off
- Privately-identifiable info never referenced

**[IF manufacturing / industrial]:**
- Cite certifications only if current
- No capacity claims beyond verified throughput
- Customer + supplier names typically confidential

